<paragraph id="E97036DD3F70FFE7FF26FF11FCF4FF1B" blockId="69.[151,1437,151,250]" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">
Geographic distribution. Mediterranean and Atlantic Ocean. In the Mediterranean, known from the northern coast from Alboran Sea to Levant, and also on the south coast from 
<collectingCountry id="91D8764D3F70FFE7FC6EFF3DFC03FF34" box="[911,995,187,213]" name="Algeria" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">Algeria</collectingCountry>
(Miller 1986). In the Atlantic Ocean, it was recorded from 
<collectingCountry id="91D8764D3F70FFE7FE91FF59FE35FF18" box="[368,469,223,249]" name="Morocco" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">Morocco</collectingCountry>
and Canaries (Miller 1986).
</paragraph>
